{"tid":1635223,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"日日都係全民口罩日","createTime":"2019-10-07T12:33:40.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-07T17:07:19.000Z","uid":41744,"like":12,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"97f249db996f94981a287197f981022c04449498","tid":1635223,"uid":41744,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T12:33:40.000Z","msg":"返工返學睇戲行街<br />\n同我帶爆佢<br />\n返工唔得就係返工既路途上帶"},{"pid":"c82b0e40f2731f96cb06ff51a06830807d5e1f8b","tid":1635223,"uid":41744,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T12:34:09.000Z","msg":"屌開錯波台<br />\n睇波都要帶"},{"pid":"567ff3e568c8388ebf3ce1b378111c3e3b53688d","tid":1635223,"uid":160842,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T12:39:04.000Z","msg":"勿拆黨鐵！！全民被罷工！！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1633581\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1633581</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n罷工係對個政權最撚有衝擊既抗爭手法，但三罷做左咁撚多次，都係得8.5成功，因為計劃左好撚耐，對香港人黎講，個個都只想被罷工，到呢個地步，你仲想做休息撚，而唔乘勝追擊？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n三樣香港人應同樣憎恨既野：<br />\n政府、黑警、黨鐵<br />\n<br />\n呢三樣先係主線<br />\n你個啲乜鳩紅藍店，我理撚得你幾時搞？<br />\n個啲要休息，冇問題，但咁撚樣都唔食住上，令到全港自動罷工，咁我真係代表我全力支持既香港政府多謝你為香港既經濟服務<br />\n<br />\n唔撚係話和理非冇用，但勇和齊上齊落唔撚得？"},{"pid":"347e215fb85308b55cf2441b881a01a2ca341648","tid":1635223,"uid":307619,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T12:39:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Dr8yy2u.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDr8yy2u.jpg&h=ae62f083&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n咁少嘢都唔做？"},{"pid":"16f57a7db4b5c42310039a657ffa530b482efe22","tid":1635223,"uid":154040,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T13:40:53.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"d24b9949c94cd77418f21affc49222c9024c4f4c","tid":1635223,"uid":92885,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T13:42:44.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"fd264ae311b900e06576284a0e7a02d2b9463a82","tid":1635223,"u